- **Unordered list**: search $O(N)$, insert $O(1)$, remove $O(N)$. Không hỗ trợ ordered iteration.
- **Ordered list**: search $O(N)$, insert $O(N)$, remove $O(N)$. Có ordered iteration.
- **Ordered array + Binary Search**: search $O(\log_2 N)$, insert $O(N)$ (phải dời), remove $O(N)$.
- **Sequential search** — $N/2$ compares trung bình:
```cpp
Value seqsearch(int l, int r, Key key) {
    for (int i = l; i <= r; i++)
        if (keys[i] == key) return values[i];
    return nullValue;
}
```
- **Binary search** — $\leq \log_2(N+1)$ compares:
```cpp
Value binsearch(int l, int r, Key key) {
    do {
        int m = (l + r) / 2;
        if (keys[m] == key) return values[m];
        else if (keys[m] > key) r = m - 1;
        else l = m + 1;
    } while (l <= r);
    return nullValue;
}
```
- **Interpolation search**: thay $m = l + \frac{key - keys[l]}{keys[r] - keys[l]}(r-l)$ — tốt hơn binary search khi keys phân phối đều.

code_snippet:
Value binsearch(int l, int r, Key key) {
    do {
        int m = (l + r) / 2;
        if (keys[m] == key) return values[m];
        else if (keys[m] > key) r = m {{-}} 1;
        else l = m {{+}} 1;
    } while (l <= r);
    return nullValue;
}

